      "guid": "https://themerchbooth.substack.com/p/things-that-were-good-for-me-this",
      "title": "things that were good FOR ME (!!!) this week (1/18-1/24) ",
      "link": "https://themerchbooth.substack.com/p/things-that-were-good-for-me-this",
      "pubDate": "Thu, 22 Jan 2026 22:29:34 GMT",
      "creator": "lex",
      "description": "I&#8217;m actively avoiding opening most of my apps bc the world is balls and I&#8217;m raw dogging an ever increasing level of anxiety- aka I am scared of the news and OCD is plaguing every negative thing into the grandest doom spiral.",
      "contentEncoded": "<p>I&#8217;m actively avoiding opening most of my apps bc the world is <em>balls </em>and I&#8217;m raw dogging an ever increasing level of anxiety- aka<em> I am scared of the news </em>and OCD is plaguing every negative thing into the grandest doom spiral. Just like the time when I was five and sat down at the family computer with a calculator to try and figure out how big space was. </p><p>I acknowledge I have the privilege to just turn my phone off to avoid the news at the moment, but it&#8217;s the only thing I can muster right now. </p><p>Here is what has brought <strong>SPECIFICALLY ME</strong> joy this week, if you even care. </p><h3><strong>Animal Crossing New Horizons 3.0 Update</strong></h3><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!0Dio!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc5a34c7b-ce3f-4d52-ab72-2ec8f65e39b3_882x665.jpeg\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!0Dio!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc5a34c7b-ce3f-4d52-ab72-2ec8f65e39b3_882x665.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!0Dio!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc5a34c7b-ce3f-4d52-ab72-2ec8f65e39b3_882x665.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!0Dio!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc5a34c7b-ce3f-4d52-ab72-2ec8f65e39b3_882x665.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!0Dio!,w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc5a34c7b-ce3f-4d52-ab72-2ec8f65e39b3_882x665.jpeg 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!0Dio!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc5a34c7b-ce3f-4d52-ab72-2ec8f65e39b3_882x665.jpeg\" width=\"882\" height=\"665\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/c5a34c7b-ce3f-4d52-ab72-2ec8f65e39b3_882x665.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:&quot;normal&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:665,&quot;width&quot;:882,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:0,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" class=\"sizing-normal\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!0Dio!,w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc5a34c7b-ce3f-4d52-ab72-2ec8f65e39b3_882x665.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!0Dio!,w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc5a34c7b-ce3f-4d52-ab72-2ec8f65e39b3_882x665.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!0Dio!,w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc5a34c7b-ce3f-4d52-ab72-2ec8f65e39b3_882x665.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!0Dio!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc5a34c7b-ce3f-4d52-ab72-2ec8f65e39b3_882x665.jpeg 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><div class=\"image-link-expand\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\"><button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\"><svg role=\"img\" style=\"height:20px;width:20px\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><g><title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path></g></svg></button><button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\"><polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line></svg></button></div></div></div></a></figure></div><p>I, like every other unemployed queer who owns a Nintendo Switch, am utterly locked tf into Animal Crossing again like it is 3/20/2020. </p><p>I have a dog and a cat, a garden, have a full actual house in REAL LIFE for the first time and yet all I wanna do is run around and garden on my make believe island with the animals who inhabit it under my cold, tyrannical rule. </p><p>Most importantly, with the aid of the Legend of Zelda amiibo figures I stole from my little brother&#8217;s, I can now invite the two new coolest anthropomorphic lesbians to my village for a little more pizzazz.</p><p>I have been playing Animal Crossing since 2002 when my older brother and I received it as a gift on GameCube. I have never fully upgraded my house, but like The Sims, I have logged thousands of hours into the plotlines I have in my head.</p><h3><strong>ALTON BROWN IS NOT DEAD </strong></h3><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!PNIW!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5dfcc208-5d28-4ed4-bb75-a2b5528f600f_1206x2622.jpeg\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!PNIW!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5dfcc208-5d28-4ed4-bb75-a2b5528f600f_1206x2622.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!PNIW!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5dfcc208-5d28-4ed4-bb75-a2b5528f600f_1206x2622.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!PNIW!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5dfcc208-5d28-4ed4-bb75-a2b5528f600f_1206x2622.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!PNIW!,w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5dfcc208-5d28-4ed4-bb75-a2b5528f600f_1206x2622.jpeg 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!PNIW!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5dfcc208-5d28-4ed4-bb75-a2b5528f600f_1206x2622.jpeg\" width=\"1206\" height=\"2622\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/5dfcc208-5d28-4ed4-bb75-a2b5528f600f_1206x2622.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:&quot;normal&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:2622,&quot;width&quot;:1206,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:0,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" class=\"sizing-normal\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!PNIW!,w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5dfcc208-5d28-4ed4-bb75-a2b5528f600f_1206x2622.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!PNIW!,w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5dfcc208-5d28-4ed4-bb75-a2b5528f600f_1206x2622.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!PNIW!,w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5dfcc208-5d28-4ed4-bb75-a2b5528f600f_1206x2622.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!PNIW!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5dfcc208-5d28-4ed4-bb75-a2b5528f600f_1206x2622.jpeg 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" loading=\"lazy\"></picture><div class=\"image-link-expand\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\"><button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\"><svg role=\"img\" style=\"height:20px;width:20px\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><g><title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path></g></svg></button><button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\"><polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line></svg></button></div></div></div></a></figure></div><p>I remember being really sad in like 2020 because <strong>Alton Brown had died</strong>. This was like, right after my grandmother had passed, and <em>Good Eats </em>was our shit. When I&#8217;d spend my weekends at her house and she&#8217;d pour me a glass of wine with our 8pm dinner (mind you I was like 11) because that&#8217;s &#8220;how the Europeans did it&#8221; in front of the little kitchen counter TV, we&#8217;d watch Good Eats. That&#8217;s how I learned to cook! </p><p>Also all gay millennials/Z-ers had a Food Network phase, and if you didn&#8217;t you&#8217;re lying. </p><p>Imagine my surprise when I was scrolling TikTok, and someone&#8217;s fancast for a new season of <em>Traitors</em> included Mr.Brown next to the likes of Katya and Honey Boo Boo. I was like &#8220;oh bummer that would rip.&#8221; All the comments are like &#8220;YESSS ALTON WOULD BE SO GOOD&#8221; and I was like &#8220;closest we could get is Sam Reich&#8221; </p><p>BITCH COME TO FIND OUT??? ALTON IS ALIVE AND WELL!!!! NOT IN MY TIMELINE!!!</p><h3><strong>MIKA&#8217;s &#8220;Hyperlove&#8221; Releases</strong></h3><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!db1l!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F568be2e4-78e1-4d17-bcf8-991ffe61ed78_1024x1024.jpeg\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!db1l!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F568be2e4-78e1-4d17-bcf8-991ffe61ed78_1024x1024.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!db1l!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F568be2e4-78e1-4d17-bcf8-991ffe61ed78_1024x1024.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!db1l!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F568be2e4-78e1-4d17-bcf8-991ffe61ed78_1024x1024.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!db1l!,w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F568be2e4-78e1-4d17-bcf8-991ffe61ed78_1024x1024.jpeg 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!db1l!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F568be2e4-78e1-4d17-bcf8-991ffe61ed78_1024x1024.jpeg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/568be2e4-78e1-4d17-bcf8-991ffe61ed78_1024x1024.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:&quot;normal&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:1024,&quot;width&quot;:1024,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:0,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" class=\"sizing-normal\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!db1l!,w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F568be2e4-78e1-4d17-bcf8-991ffe61ed78_1024x1024.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!db1l!,w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F568be2e4-78e1-4d17-bcf8-991ffe61ed78_1024x1024.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!db1l!,w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F568be2e4-78e1-4d17-bcf8-991ffe61ed78_1024x1024.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!db1l!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F568be2e4-78e1-4d17-bcf8-991ffe61ed78_1024x1024.jpeg 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" loading=\"lazy\"></picture><div class=\"image-link-expand\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\"><button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\"><svg role=\"img\" style=\"height:20px;width:20px\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><g><title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path></g></svg></button><button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\"><polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line></svg></button></div></div></div></a></figure></div><p>Technically this happens in two hours, but one of my  favorite artists will release his 7th(?) studio album and I am puuuumped. I have known of MIKA for twenty years, and have officially been a fan since 2010 when Kick Ass was released.  </p><p>Every important milestone in my life has been marked by a new MIKA album- it is like law that has been set by my universe. This new chapter is the one where I now live in Italy, and people know who I&#8217;m talking about when I mention his name- he&#8217;s <em>THE SHIT </em>here!!! </p><p>Apparently, this record is the closest to his OG sound he&#8217;s been in years. I (and the teenage me replaying his music videos over and over on my iPod) cannot wait.</p><h3><strong>FABLE XBOX Developer Direct </strong></h3><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!LH4i!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3cb8e1eb-eb67-476c-878f-d1acae941eb0_1080x607.jpeg\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!LH4i!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3cb8e1eb-eb67-476c-878f-d1acae941eb0_1080x607.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!LH4i!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3cb8e1eb-eb67-476c-878f-d1acae941eb0_1080x607.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!LH4i!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3cb8e1eb-eb67-476c-878f-d1acae941eb0_1080x607.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!LH4i!,w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3cb8e1eb-eb67-476c-878f-d1acae941eb0_1080x607.jpeg 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!LH4i!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3cb8e1eb-eb67-476c-878f-d1acae941eb0_1080x607.jpeg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"607\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/3cb8e1eb-eb67-476c-878f-d1acae941eb0_1080x607.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:&quot;normal&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:607,&quot;width&quot;:1080,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:0,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" class=\"sizing-normal\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!LH4i!,w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3cb8e1eb-eb67-476c-878f-d1acae941eb0_1080x607.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!LH4i!,w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3cb8e1eb-eb67-476c-878f-d1acae941eb0_1080x607.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!LH4i!,w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3cb8e1eb-eb67-476c-878f-d1acae941eb0_1080x607.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!LH4i!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3cb8e1eb-eb67-476c-878f-d1acae941eb0_1080x607.jpeg 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" loading=\"lazy\"></picture><div class=\"image-link-expand\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\"><button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\"><svg role=\"img\" style=\"height:20px;width:20px\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><g><title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path></g></svg></button><button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\"><polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line></svg></button></div></div></div></a></figure></div><p>This week has been so huge for a younger me. Fable is <strong>back</strong>. Finally. I was first introduced to the og Xbox title in my next door neighbor&#8217;s basement, and as an obnoxious, young Anglophile, I fell in love. 2005, I think? </p><p>With humo<em><strong>u</strong></em>r akin to Monty Python, equally as crude and just as immature and silly, this series of fantasy RPGs is a staple in my game library. Truly, this was the start of my online lore. IYKYK.</p><p>The first look is nuts. I am intrigued by the drop of the morality system (if your choices were &#8220;bad&#8221; in the old games, physically you morph into a demon) and moving towards a more involved judgement based system. Basically, when I become a landlord, the people are gonna hate me! I am excited! </p><p>Even though this reboot seems to take place prior to my favorite character Reaver&#8217;s timeline, I hope he is mentioned or prophesied. He&#8217;s a bisexual pirate king. Now you know why I loved the game. </p><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!78nt!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe56a70da-dab0-4b15-9d19-855ca1370d48_1280x720.jpeg\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!78nt!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe56a70da-dab0-4b15-9d19-855ca1370d48_1280x720.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!78nt!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe56a70da-dab0-4b15-9d19-855ca1370d48_1280x720.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!78nt!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe56a70da-dab0-4b15-9d19-855ca1370d48_1280x720.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!78nt!,w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe56a70da-dab0-4b15-9d19-855ca1370d48_1280x720.jpeg 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!78nt!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe56a70da-dab0-4b15-9d19-855ca1370d48_1280x720.jpeg\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/e56a70da-dab0-4b15-9d19-855ca1370d48_1280x720.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:&quot;normal&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:720,&quot;width&quot;:1280,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:0,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" class=\"sizing-normal\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!78nt!,w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe56a70da-dab0-4b15-9d19-855ca1370d48_1280x720.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!78nt!,w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe56a70da-dab0-4b15-9d19-855ca1370d48_1280x720.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!78nt!,w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe56a70da-dab0-4b15-9d19-855ca1370d48_1280x720.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!78nt!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe56a70da-dab0-4b15-9d19-855ca1370d48_1280x720.jpeg 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" loading=\"lazy\"></picture><div class=\"image-link-expand\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\"><button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\"><svg role=\"img\" style=\"height:20px;width:20px\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><g><title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path></g></svg></button><button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\"><polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line></svg></button></div></div></div></a></figure></div><h3><strong>RAPID ROUND:</strong></h3><p><strong>Harry Styles</strong> emerged from his gay ass little Roman fuck chrysalis with Zo&#235; Kravitz and released the ill-designed cover of his <strong>next album</strong>, which means ABBA inspired fast fashion will live another concert season.  And Baby, I LOVE disco. </p><p><strong>Jennette McCurdy&#8217;s new book</strong> released today, and there is hope that I will read and complete my first fiction novel in almost ten years(?) I hope to break free of my autobiographical cocoon. </p><p>I am addicted to making <strong>little sauces</strong> with my meals. I almost exclusively eat a combination of (my safe foods) rice (&#128525;), meat (chicken, ground turkey or beef), and 9 times out of 10 broccoli. Recently, I have gotten back into sweet potatoes (and apparently so has the internet). I am enjoying them with a combo of Soy Sauce/Honey/ACV/Dijon Mustard/Ground Ginger/Brown Sugar</p><p>Girls are showcasing their <strong>bum ass</strong> behaviored <strong>ex-boyfriends</strong> as part of a trend on <strong>TikTok</strong>, and it&#8217;s so fun to watch people <em>see the light. </em>If your man wears a rank ass stinky ass mildewy medallion and didn&#8217;t have a bed frame until you were boning on the reg, DUMP HIM! Fun fun fun! </p><p>I went to Venice on Sunday, walked 10 miles, and <strong>did NOT smoke a cigarette</strong> even though everyone else was and they looked really hot and cool while doing it. I never picked up the analog habit but I haven&#8217;t vaped in ~6 months &amp; haven&#8217;t had a Zyn in about two. (I have like four canisters I never got to, waiting in my office if the urge ever arises again) They will come with me when I go back on tour.  That is when I will pick the habit back up realistically lol. </p><p>I think <strong>Nicole</strong> is going to be rehired at <strong>Bistro Huddy</strong> within the week- scenes were having me stressed. Shhh my stories are on. </p><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!iSmC!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa37da846-ac0d-465c-8d1b-14cca9eeb060_250x274.jpeg\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!iSmC!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa37da846-ac0d-465c-8d1b-14cca9eeb060_250x274.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!iSmC!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa37da846-ac0d-465c-8d1b-14cca9eeb060_250x274.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!iSmC!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa37da846-ac0d-465c-8d1b-14cca9eeb060_250x274.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!iSmC!,w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa37da846-ac0d-465c-8d1b-14cca9eeb060_250x274.jpeg 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!iSmC!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa37da846-ac0d-465c-8d1b-14cca9eeb060_250x274.jpeg\" width=\"250\" height=\"274\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/a37da846-ac0d-465c-8d1b-14cca9eeb060_250x274.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&qu